name: testHelpForFeatureButton
description: Verify that when you click the 'Pipeline: Multibranch' link after clicking the 'Help for Feature: Script Path', you are taken to the 'Pipeline: Multibranch' page
descriptionHtml: Verify that when you click the 'Pipeline: Multibranch' link after clicking the 'Help for Feature: Script Path', you are taken to the 'Pipeline: Multibranch' page

testStage.description: Verify that when you click the 'Pipeline: Multibranch' link after clicking the 'Help for Feature: Script Path', you are taken to the 'Pipeline: Multibranch' page

steps.name: Click on 'New Item' in the side menu
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Click 'Logo' button and move to main page
Click on the 'Configure' button on side menu
Click on the 'Configure' Button on the Base Job Page
Click on the 'Build Configuration' button on the Configuration page to select the option
Click on the 'ScriptPath' button on the Build Configuration menu
Click on the 'Pipeline: Multibranch' link in the Script Path field to navigate to the 'Pipeline: Multibranch' page
Switch to the Workflow Multibranch page in the other window
Get title from the Workflow Multibranch page
